creator: bringo
descriptionHtml:
Bringo is an ordering and delivery service where you can arrange food delivery from cafes and restaurants.

You can easily choose and order delicious, hot and appetizing food from various catering establishments in Tashkent, and get your order at your convenience.

Our mission is to improve the lifestyle of consumers by providing better and convenient access to quality food.

Treat yourself, your loved ones with original or traditional meals, surprise guests with exclusive dishes from the best metropolitan chefs, right at home or in the office, without wasting time and effort on cooking.

You can order food from restaurants and cafes urgently or on time.
The time of delivery of food (urgent or order at a time) depends on the time of cooking and the distance to the landmark of the delivery place. The price of delivery is calculated automatically when choosing a landmark.

Acceptance of orders and delivery is carried out only in Tashkent.
Order and delivery service "Bringo" ensures that your order is delivered on time.

Payment method you can pre-select during the order process. Payment is accepted in cash, upon receipt of the order. In addition, in some establishments you can pay for your order through other types of payments.
descriptionShort: 24-hour food delivery in Tashkent. Delicious and hot dishes from the restaurants

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New improved design
- Easy search on the map
- Possibility to change data in your account

Description:
The new app has become even more convenient to use; technical problems have been fixed and the app has become faster. The design has become even more modern and user-friendly. Search on the map has been improved not only for the nearest restaurants but also for restaurants at a distance, which allows you to make an order remotely. Now it is easy to manage your account and edit your data.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Updated design. New blocks have been added for the convenience of searching and ordering your favorite dishes. There is an opportunity to choose branches of the café or restaurant, regardless of your location. A single profile and shopping cart allow you to order from the app, website, or telegram bot and repeat your order. It is possible to leave comments, assess the quality of delivery and establishments after receiving the order. You can see the name and contact of the courier also.
